{"title":"Álex and Marc Márquez to train on Mondraker F-Podium RR XC bikes for Moto GP Season","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/02/02/alex-and-marc-marquez-to-train-on-mondraker-f-podium-rr-xc-bikes-for-moto-gp-season/","date":1612281334000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p><span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-box-3\"></span>Alex and Marc Marquez, the biggest names in Grand Prix, have partnered with Mondraker in preparation for their 2021 MotoGP Season. The brothers have each been given fully customized F-podium RR carbon cross-country bikes which they plan to use for cardio training. With a paint job and decals to match Marc’s MotoGP helmet and Repsol Honda Team motorbike, Mondraker may want to consider adding a new colorway to the line.</p><h2>Marquez Brothers’ Mondraker F-Podium RR Bikes</h2><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/marc-marquez-checks-out-his-new-mondraker-bike.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/marc-marquez-checks-out-his-new-mondraker-bike.jpg\" alt=\"marc marquex mondraker f-podium rr\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/marc-marquez-checks-out-his-new-mondraker-bike.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/marc-marquez-checks-out-his-new-mondraker-bike.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/marc-marquez-checks-out-his-new-mondraker-bike-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/marc-marquez-checks-out-his-new-mondraker-bike-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdn